title: P2P Programs
description:
Some very useful apps for P2P, especially uTorrent.

Included are:

Block List Manager
P2P Connection Patch
Peer Guardian 2
uTorrent 1.77
uTorrent CHM file (Help)
Bit-Che
Bittorrent Ultra Accelerator


All are described in the included text file, and with direct links if possible.

These have all made a difference in my download speeds and blocking of unwanted sites.
